long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension is constantly updated regardless of the update date on this page, so the extension is always relevant regardless of the current version of the game, FIFA 25 or later.

Premium content:
- SBC Solver
- Autobuyer
- Autoseller
- Club analysis
- FutBin SBC import
- FutBin/FUT.GG prices data
- Enchanced interface
Free content:
- Shortcuts
- EA tax in interface
- «Open card on FutBin» button
- «Find min BIN» button
- Hot links
